        ; FLOOR_SPRITE_IDX payload ($1E00-$1EFF, 256 bytes).
        ;
        ; Maps a floor-position index to a 7-frame sprite-frame index
        ; ($00..$06).  Layout is a 28-byte cyclic ramp: four copies
        ; each of 0..6, repeated nine times, tailing off with four
        ; zeros (9*28 + 4 = 256).  Every four floor steps advance one
        ; sprite frame, producing the walk-cycle animation as the
        ; player's (or enemy's) floor position scrolls past.
