; --- $5DE4-$5DEF -> $03E4-$03EF: RESCUE_COUNTDOWN head (12 bytes) ---
; FIRST_BOOT's 240-byte copy ends at $5DEF inclusive; these 12 bytes
; form the RESCUE_COUNTDOWN head ($03E4-$03EF).  The corresponding
