        HEX 1A 2A 04 05 09 02 04 10
        HEX 1E 09 04
L1_RESCUE_DRIFT_PITCH:
        ; $0213-$0217 (5 bytes): RESCUE_DRIFT_PITCH drift-mode pitch.
        HEX 07 0C 10 13 15
L1_SND_PITCH_TBL_SPECIAL:
        ; $0218-$0223 (12 bytes): ascending pitch for special-sprite
        ; sfx; last 5 bytes double as SND_PITCH_TBL_SPECIAL_B.
