[[L1_BEAM_TARGET_DRAW_TAIL]] & tail of [[BEAM_TARGET_DRAW]] & [[$1300]]--[[$1309]] & 10 & on-hit bookkeeping + slot-loop tail \\
[[L1_BEAM_UPDATE]] & [[BEAM_UPDATE]] & [[$130A]]--[[$13A3]] & 154 & per-frame beam target + tracer update \\
[[L1_GAME_START_INIT]] & [[GAME_START_INIT]] & [[$13A4]]--[[$13D5]] & 50 & re-entry after life-lost / level-start \\
